#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn12.47"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.47:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.47:0.2"
msgid "5. Gahapativagga "
msgstr "5. Householders "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 47. Jāṇussoṇisutta → jānussoṇi (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn12.47:0.3"
msgid "47. Jāṇussoṇisutta "
msgstr "47. Jāṇussoṇi "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn12.47:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.47:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the brahmin Jāṇussoṇi went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with him. Seated to one side he said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn12.47:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ nu kho, bho gotama, sabbamatthī”ti? "
msgstr "“Master Gotama, does all exist?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.47:2.2"
msgid "“‘Sabbamatthī’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, ayameko anto”. "
msgstr "“‘All exists’: this is one extreme, brahmin.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn12.47:3.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ pana, bho gotama, sabbaṃ natthī”ti? "
msgstr "“Then does all not exist?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.47:3.2"
msgid "“‘Sabbaṃ natthī’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, ayaṃ dutiyo anto. "
msgstr "“‘All doesn’t exist’: this is the second extreme. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.47:3.3"
msgid "Ete te, brāhmaṇa, ubho ante anupagamma majjhena tathāgato dhammaṃ deseti: "
msgstr "Avoiding these two extremes, the Realized One teaches by the middle way: "

msgctxt "sn12.47:3.4"
msgid "‘avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā; "
msgstr "‘Ignorance is a condition for choices. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.47:3.5"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Choices are a condition for consciousness. … "

msgctxt "sn12.47:3.6"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. "
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates. "

msgctxt "sn12.47:3.7"
msgid "Avijjāya tveva asesavirāganirodhā saṅkhāranirodho; "
msgstr "When ignorance fades away and ceases with nothing left over, choices cease. "

msgctxt "sn12.47:3.8"
msgid "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho … pe … "
msgstr "When choices cease, consciousness ceases. … "

msgctxt "sn12.47:3.9"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī’”ti. "
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.77, sc4
msgctxt "sn12.47:4.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, the brahmin Jāṇussoṇi said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn12.47:4.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! … "

msgctxt "sn12.47:4.3"
msgid "pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.47:4.4"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

